						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">6502freak wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Ambitious developers most certainly don't rely on mappers. They work on the gameplay until it's perfected. [...] Like I said, people gravely underestimate how much work went into the DESIGN of those games. Adjusting the game mechanics until they play perfectly.</div>
